# New Feature Requests

## 1. Multi-Language Support with Language Detection
Add automatic language detection based on user's browser settings and allow users to switch languages manually. Include translations for more languages beyond English (Spanish, French, Portuguese, Swahili, etc.).

## 2. Push Notifications System
Implement web push notifications for:
- New events and sermon announcements
- Prayer request updates
- Live stream alerts
- Attendance reminders
- Group/message notifications

## 3. Mobile App Wrapper (PWA Enhancements)
- Add offline support for devotionals and Bible reading
- Add "Add to Home Screen" prompt
- Implement background sync for when connection is restored
- Add app install banner with custom branding

## 4. Advanced Member Directory with Search & Filters
- Advanced search by name, role, house cell, parish
- Filter by membership date range
- Member profile cards with quick actions
- Export members to CSV/PDF
- Member activity timeline

## 5. Automated Email & SMS Notifications
- Welcome emails for new members
- Event reminder emails/SMS
- Birthday and anniversary celebrations
- Weekly devotional digest
- Attendance follow-up emails

## 6. Financial Dashboard & Reports
- Tithes and offerings tracking
- Generate income/expense reports
- Receipt generation for donations
- Goal tracking for fundraising campaigns
- Export financial reports to PDF/Excel

## 7. Prayer Wall Feature
- Public prayer wall where members can post prayer requests
- Allow anonymous prayer requests
- Prayer countdown/completion tracking
- Prayer warrior assignment system
- Weekly prayer digest emails

## 8. Event Calendar Integration
- Sync with Google Calendar, Outlook, Apple Calendar
- Add to calendar buttons on all events
- Recurring event support
- Event categories and tags
- Event feedback/rating system

## 9. Small Group Management System
- Create and manage Bible study groups
- Group hierarchy (zones, sectors, cells)
- Group leader assignment and training tracking
- Group meeting scheduler
- Group resources sharing

## 10. Content Management System (CMS) for Pages
- Customizable landing pages
- About Us, Contact, FAQ pages
- Staff/leadership team page
- Photo gallery management
- Announcement banners

## 11. Attendance Heatmaps & Analytics
- Visual attendance heatmaps by service/time
- Member engagement scoring
- At-risk member identification
- Attendance prediction alerts
- Trend analysis charts

## 12. Online Giving & Payments Integration
- Recurring giving setup
- Multiple payment methods (card, bank transfer, USSD)
- Giving goals and campaigns
- Tax receipt generation
- Giving history and statements

## 13. Member Check-in Kiosk Mode
- Dedicated kiosk interface for church entrances
- QR code scanning for quick check-in
- Guest registration form
- Family/household check-in
- Temperature check integration option

## 14. Chat & Messaging System
- Direct messaging between members
- Group chats for ministries
- Broadcast messages from admins
- Read receipts and typing indicators
- Message templates

## 15. Resource Library
- Sermon notes and transcripts
- Teaching materials download
- Church policies and documents
- Video and audio archives
- Searchable content database
